born with all our eggs.

13:43.834 --> 13:45.459
I feel so crummy.

13:47.292 --> 13:49.500
Pregnancy's not good for you.

13:50.167 --> 13:52.167
- And look at our mothers.
- (CHUCKLES)

13:54.292 --> 13:56.292
You've always had it in
for your mum, haven't you?

13:58.417 --> 13:59.459
Me?

14:00.250 --> 14:01.417
Morty?

14:02.875 --> 14:05.459
