since the day I was conceived.

14:08.125 --> 14:09.334
(SIGHS)

14:16.292 --> 14:17.292
(CHUCKLES)

14:20.167 --> 14:22.209
Gin and a knitting needle.

14:23.250 --> 14:25.584
- Yeah.
- (GROANS)

14:33.125 --> 14:34.709
I'm definitely bigger.

14:35.334 --> 14:37.042
They're killing me.

14:37.250 --> 14:38.667
(DOOR OPENS)

14:43.250 --> 14:44.917
- You've changed.
- (CHUCKLES)

14:45.000 --> 14:47.209
Did we extend the invitation?

14:56.709 --> 14:58.459
It'll loosen you up, Crazy Face.

14:58.792 --> 14:59.959
I don't wanna be loose.

15:05.000 --> 15:06.667
Oh, nice.

15:12.334 --> 15:15.334
"Everything that lives
serves the purposes of the earth.

15:15.417 --> 15:17.667
"Everything that dies serves the moon."

15:19.084 --> 15:20.167
KENNETH: Hmm?

15:21.000 --> 15:22.667
- You know I'm pregnant.
- (SIGHS)

15:23.167 --> 15:25.125
- She's telling everyone.
- You're in trouble?

15:25.209 --> 15:26.209
Kenneth!

15:27.750 --> 15:29.334
Let's do some magick,

15:30.500 --> 15:32.959
with a K, to dispel it.

15:33.167 --> 15:34.625
I could do a spell.

15:34.709 --> 15:36.509
LYDIA: Oh, yeah?
When's that ever worked, hmm?

15:36.542 --> 15:38.375
KENNETH: You know,
most people think it's bad,

15:38.875 --> 15:41.375
but all the occult actually
means is "hidden".

15:41.459 --> 15:42.459
LYDIA: Ooh.

15:42.542 --> 15:45.709
On a more practical note,

15:46.542 --> 15:47.917
a bit of

15:50.084 --> 15:52.917
vigorous exercise might get rid of it.

15:56.084 --> 15:57.709
Let's go dancing.

15:58.500 --> 15:59.542
Yeah.

16:00.000 --> 16:01.000
Where?

16:02.500 --> 16:03.584
Not far.

16:04.084 --> 16:06.084
