(GRUNTING)

17:50.625 --> 17:52.042
(DOOR CREAKS OPEN)

18:02.209 --> 18:03.334
Lamb.

18:10.084 --> 18:13.042
This situation has made you
so unpredictable.

18:13.292 --> 18:14.625
I'm sorry.

18:15.584 --> 18:17.250
I don't know what came over me.

18:23.459 --> 18:24.459
It's just...

18:25.209 --> 18:26.500
You're...

18:28.292 --> 18:31.625
- You know, everything and...
- And vice versa.

18:33.084 --> 18:35.334
It didn't mean a thing, truly.

18:36.334 --> 18:37.417
(SCOFFS)

18:37.625 --> 18:39.292
It's only Kenneth.

18:45.417 --> 18:47.792
He went on about the
laws of love, you know.

18:48.375 --> 18:49.709
Free love. (CHUCKLES)

18:57.667 --> 18:59.917
- And you told Susan about your situation.
- (CHUCKLES)

19:00.000 --> 19:03.875
I wanted shock on that
innocent little face.

19:07.834 --> 19:09.375
(BOTH GIGGLING)

19:18.125 --> 19:20.459
I think I've wet myself.

19:23.542 --> 19:24.834
Maybe you're losing it.

19:26.917 --> 19:28.125
No, it's...

19:28.834 --> 19:30.625
It's just a bit of...

19:31.209 --> 19:32.500
You know.

19:38.292 --> 19:40.959
He said the French call an orgasm
a small death.

19:43.125 --> 19:44.792
That's what it's like, you know.

19:45.709 --> 19:47.709
When a guy's inside you
and you get it right.

19:49.667 --> 19:51.250
Feels like you're blacking out.

19:52.792 --> 19:53.959
Dying.

20:08.084 --> 20:09.084
(CHUCKLES)

20:44.709 --> 20:46.209
(BELL RINGING)

20:47.000 --> 20:48.750
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

21:07.542 --> 21:09.625
(WRITING ON BLACKBOARD)

21:24.417 --> 21:26.584
Abigail Mortimer

21:26.667 --> 21:29.875
and Lydia Lamont.

21:30.834 --> 21:32.167
Detention.

21:36.584 --> 21:40.209
During the war
I always managed to arrive on time.

21:42.375 --> 21:44.709
Even contending with doodlebugs.

21:48.042 --> 21:52.209
One day you'll realise that even you,

21:52.542 --> 21:53.750
Abigail,

21:55.334 --> 21:57.042
are living history.

22:06.375 --> 22:07.459
(VOMITING)

22:07.542 --> 22:10.709
Oh, for crying out loud! Oh...

22:11.917 --> 22:13.625
Janet, go and get a mop.

22:17.917 --> 22:19.667
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

22:26.250 --> 22:27.500
Shame to waste it.

22:38.292 --> 22:41.459
Do you think it tastes metallic?

22:41.709 --> 22:45.417
That happened when my mum was pregnant.

22:47.334 --> 22:48.542
(ABBIE SIGHS)

22:51.667 --> 22:53.125
I didn't say anything.

22:54.792 --> 22:55.792
(GIGGLES)

22:56.209 --> 23:00.709
According to Lydia,
my body has become a situation.

23:01.917 --> 23:04.709
We'll soon be dealing with the situation.

23:05.000 --> 23:07.042
You're not gonna get rid of it yourselves?

23:07.125 --> 23:08.625
We've got it under control.

23:08.709 --> 23:11.959
It's not passed you by its legal nowadays?

23:12.042 --> 23:13.375
Not for the likes of us.

24:00.000 --> 24:01.709
- Abbie?
- (GASPS)

24:08.167 --> 24:09.667
(ABBIE CHUCKLES)

24:25.084 --> 24:30.459
So, you will each
learn these recipes off by heart.

24:30.542 --> 24:32.792
Can't we learn a poem instead, Miss Mantel?

24:32.875 --> 24:33.917
No.

24:36.334 --> 24:37.959
I'll be back shortly.

24:39.542 --> 24:40.542
(DOOR CLOSES)

24:40.750 --> 24:41.959
(SIGHS)

24:45.084 --> 24:46.750
Her breath stinks.

24:48.542 --> 24:51.667
Puking up on her is probably
the most attention she's ever had.

24:51.750 --> 24:52.792
(LAUGHS)

24:52.875 --> 24:53.917
Never lived.

24:54.000 --> 24:55.375
(LYDIA SIGHS)

24:56.209 --> 24:58.750
"Savoury turnovers make a tasty dish

24:58.834 --> 25:01.750
"and a pleasant change
from the ordinary fare..."

25:01.834 --> 25:03.500
I keep thinking about keeping it.

25:05.750 --> 25:07.375
I know you don't want it.

25:09.250 --> 25:11.542
I'll get medical books
from the library, Morty.

25:12.084 --> 25:13.417
Nothing will go wrong.

25:13.834 --> 25:14.917
I know.

25:15.917 --> 25:17.292
It's just a feeling.

25:17.375 --> 25:19.125
But you can't trust feelings.

25:19.459 --> 25:21.334
We're not kids any more, Lamb.

25:21.750 --> 25:23.750
We've got to face up to it.
There's a real world out here.

25:23.834 --> 25:26.542
Yeah, and you're the centre of it.

25:26.625 --> 25:29.625
- What's that?
- All this because he had a car.

25:30.875 --> 25:32.334
And what the hell was Kenneth?

25:33.542 --> 25:35.125
He's my brother.

25:35.917 --> 25:38.417
Why is doing it so important to you anyway?

25:38.875 --> 25:40.167
I don't get it.

25:40.459 --> 25:42.084
I feel so crummy.

25:47.750 --> 25:52.125
I can't focus properly, Miss Mantel.
Honestly, I feel so awful.

25:52.209 --> 25:53.209
(DOOR CLOSES)

25:53.292 --> 25:54.709
MISS MANTEL: For crying out loud!

25:54.792 --> 25:55.917
(MISS MANTEL SIGHS)

25:56.667 --> 26:00.667
Oh, I have better things
to do with my time than this.

26:00.750 --> 26:02.084
Out! Out!

26:06.292 --> 26:07.375
(DOOR CLOSES)

26:32.750 --> 26:34.417
Say something, please.

26:34.875 --> 26:37.292
We'll always be, whatever happens.

26:37.375 --> 26:38.917
What do you want me to say?

26:39.000 --> 26:40.084
I'm sure you have something in mind.

26:40.167 --> 26:42.625
You always seem to these days.
You even sided with my mother.

26:42.709 --> 26:44.500
Oh, don't be like that.

26:44.584 --> 26:45.584
Come on!

26:45.667 --> 26:48.334
I know she's awful.
Please, I'm really not up for a fight.

26:48.417 --> 26:49.750
Admit it.

26:49.834 --> 26:51.250
You think we're over.

26:52.500 --> 26:53.709
Say it.

26:54.917 --> 26:57.625
You're getting it up
and I'm not right any more.

26:58.959 --> 27:01.584
- I'm feeling...
- You and your feelings!

27:01.792 --> 27:03.959
Millions of women have had babies, Abbie.

27:04.209 --> 27:06.750
It's nothing special. It's life.

27:07.625 --> 27:08.875
And life only.

27:11.375 --> 27:12.542
Abbie?

27:20.459 --> 27:21.625
Abbie?

27:23.625 --> 27:24.709
Abbie!

27:25.125 --> 27:26.125
Abbie!

27:27.209 --> 27:29.792
It's Lamb. It's Lydia. Come on, Abbie!

27:30.750 --> 27:33.292
Help! Please, someone!

27:33.542 --> 27:35.292
Come on! Come on, Abbie.

27:35.709 --> 27:37.000
Come on, Abbie, don't be silly.

27:37.084 --> 27:38.875
Sit up. Come on, Abbie!

27:38.959 --> 27:40.625
Someone's coming. It's gonna be fine.

27:40.709 --> 27:42.250
- MISS MANTEL: What's the matter?
- Miss Mantel!

27:42.334 --> 27:44.084
I think she's losing the baby!

27:44.792 --> 27:46.542
MISS MANTEL: Well, let her get some air!

27:48.167 --> 27:49.292
Abigail?

27:49.375 --> 27:50.417
Abigail!

27:50.500 --> 27:51.792
Get an ambulance!

27:55.542 --> 27:57.000
(GASPING)

