29:26.959 --> 29:28.542
LYDIA: Abbie!

29:30.584 --> 29:32.000
Abbie!

29:35.667 --> 29:37.125
Abbie!

29:43.417 --> 29:44.834
(DOOR OPENS)

29:58.750 --> 30:00.209
Abbie's dead.

30:01.875 --> 30:03.209
(WHIMPERS)

