It's true.

30:13.500 --> 30:14.875
She's dead.

30:27.750 --> 30:31.125
It wasn't something bad?

30:31.709 --> 30:33.042
She's dead.

30:33.125 --> 30:34.292
Well, it wasn't...

30:34.584 --> 30:36.209
- What?
- Drugs.

30:39.250 --> 30:40.792
It was natural.

30:41.584 --> 30:42.834
Natural.

30:43.667 --> 30:44.959
Abbie's young.

30:48.334 --> 30:49.917
Her poor mother.

